In the MATTER OF Corey CORBO, Union City Police Department. (Union City Police Department-Petitioner) C-941 September Term 2017
081005 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 15, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005610-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted.
